    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Affordable, driver-quality classic with plenty of charm and a great entry point for someone who wants a car to enjoy without paying top-tier money. This one is in fair overall condition, presenting as a usable, honest car that can be driven and enjoyed as-is while leaving room for cosmetic or mechanical improvement over time. A solid choice for the buyer who appreciates a straightforward classic with appeal and potential.",
