    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "$33,400 - Honest, well-kept vehicle in good overall condition. It presents nicely and has clearly been cared for, with the normal cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect for its age and use, including some minor exterior blemishes, light interior wear, and small signs of use on trim and touch points. Nothing suggests abuse, and a buyer can expect a solid, good-looking vehicle that shows well, drives as it should, and is represented accurately.",
