      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept car in good overall condition and ready to be enjoyed. It presents nicely with solid paint and body, though it does have some normal age-related cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle. The interior is clean and complete, showing some use but nothing out of line for its age. It runs and drives well, and overall it feels like a dependable driver rather than a project. This is a good, honest example for someone looking for a solid car without paying top-of-market money.",
      "price": 31900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
