      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers a practical way into ownership at a budget-friendly price. Best suited for buyers who value low upfront cost and see the opportunity in a dependable project, spare vehicle, or basic daily-use option. If you\u2019re looking for inexpensive transportation with room to make it your own, this is a compelling value.",
      "price": 4995.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runabout that could make a great budget commuter, first project, or handy spare vehicle. A straightforward option for someone who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC and wants something affordable without the big price tag. Priced to sell and worth a look if you\u2019re practical and know what you\u2019re after.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Strong project or budget driver with solid mechanical character and plenty of upside for the next owner. The engine fires up with good spirit, the transmission pulls through the gears, and the chassis still has the kind of planted feel that makes it worth saving. Cosmetically it shows wear and age, but underneath it\u2019s an honest car with usable running gear, straightforward serviceability, and real potential as a fixer-upper, commuter, or weekend restoration base. If you want an affordable entry point with good bones and enthusiast appeal, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Used, rough, priced to move. Sold as-is. $8,900 takes it.",
      "price": 8900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a machine with stories in its steel and plenty of life left for the right driver. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone who wants affordable wheels, a practical project, or a daily driver with personality instead of pretense. If you appreciate value, potential, and a car that still shows up ready for its next chapter, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
