      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical option for a buyer seeking reliable basic transportation at an approachable price. It shows its age cosmetically, but offers solid value for someone who appreciates an honest, straightforward used car without the premium price tag. A smart opportunity for commuting, a spare vehicle, or a project-minded owner.",
      "price": 5950.0,
